            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"India Economy Improves and Returns to Normal After Crisis\" data-id=\"1252243136\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1252243136/image_1252243136.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ronniechua</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Ayush Babel &amp; Jeremy Schwartz, CFA </em></p> <p>Over the past year, India has experienced a slowdown in corporate earnings growth and stock market performance, reflecting global economic headwinds, reduced government spending and softer demand across key sectors. The MSCI India Index had</p>",
